  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 6.78000020980835,
      "text": "Gotta stop that bitter, bitter fight, we're only light",
      "start": 0
    },
    {
      "end": 13.619999885559082,
      "text": "Stop that bitter, bitter fight, we're only light",
      "start": 8.279999732971191
    },
    {
      "end": 22.31999969482422,
      "text": "You gotta stop that bitter man, bitter man, bitter fuckin' fight",
      "start": 15.800000190734863
    },
    {
      "end": 25.040000915527344,
      "text": "Tonight we're all light",
      "start": 22.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 31.459999084472656,
      "text": "Stop that bitter, the bitter fight, we're all light",
      "start": 26.040000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 38.41999816894531,
      "text": "Hey, stop that, stop the bitter, the bitter talk",
      "start": 33.70000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 41.040000915527344,
      "text": "In your heart that's creepin' up",
      "start": 38.41999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 46.5,
      "text": "Inside of everything you start, the people you meet",
      "start": 42.02000045776367
    },
    {
      "end": 51.880001068115234,
      "text": "Your heart, it's bitter, make it better, come on, we're all light",
      "start": 46.5
    },
    {
      "end": 56.880001068115234,
      "text": "I knew the moment I saw you",
      "start": 51.880001068115234
    },
    {
      "end": 67.05999755859375,
      "text": "That you were the thing that's taking me through it",
      "start": 59.880001068115234
    },
    {
      "end": 74.18000030517578,
      "text": "I'm sorry the first half has made you bitter, bitter",
      "start": 68.68000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 77.30000305175781,
      "text": "You're still alive with me",
      "start": 74.18000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 83.54000091552734,
      "text": "I'm sorry you can't see the amazing thing this life",
      "start": 78.30000305175781
    },
    {
      "end": 89.04000091552734,
      "text": "Has in store for you and me, your bitter, bitter fight",
      "start": 83.54000091552734
    },
    {
      "end": 94.4000015258789,
      "text": "Take it away, we're all right, we're light tonight",
      "start": 89.04000091552734
    },
    {
      "end": 97.9800033569336,
      "text": "Hey, your bitter, bitter fuckin' fight",
      "start": 94.4000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 100.31999969482422,
      "text": "Inside your brain, we're all light",
      "start": 97.9800033569336
    },
    {
      "end": 103.95999908447266,
      "text": "Take it away from your own heat",
      "start": 100.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 113.16000366210938,
      "text": "Don't let the good burn up inside your mental ozone of defeat",
      "start": 103.95999908447266
    },
    {
      "end": 117.76000213623047,
      "text": "Nothing happened, no nothing, nothing happened, no nothing",
      "start": 113.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 121.95999908447266,
      "text": "Bitter, bitter fight, we all take the light",
      "start": 117.76000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 129.9600067138672,
      "text": "I know you hate it here with your bitter, bitter feelings",
      "start": 122.72000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 134.60000610351562,
      "text": "I'm better, feelin' better, are you better, feelin' better",
      "start": 130.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 137.5,
      "text": "Are you better, feelin' better",
      "start": 134.60000610351562
    },
    {
      "end": 147.33999633789062,
      "text": "You know I want what's best for the life you made with my strife",
      "start": 139
    },
    {
      "end": 151.33999633789062,
      "text": "But emotionally, you're just killin' me",
      "start": 147.8800048828125
    },
    {
      "end": 156.55999755859375,
      "text": "Emotionally, you don't get free",
      "start": 152.82000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 163.5800018310547,
      "text": "You think you're protectin' somethin' but that somethin' is me",
      "start": 156.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 167.74000549316406,
      "text": "Can't you see this bitter, bitter fuckin' fight",
      "start": 163.67999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 173.8800048828125,
      "text": "You fuck with me, it makes me wish I could get inside",
      "start": 167.74000549316406
    },
    {
      "end": 176.94000244140625,
      "text": "That darkness you call in your brain",
      "start": 173.8800048828125
    },
    {
      "end": 179.66000366210938,
      "text": "It's this bitter, bitter feelin'",
      "start": 176.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 185.05999755859375,
      "text": "We are the light, you gotta take those bitter, bitter feelin'",
      "start": 179.75999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 188.33999633789062,
      "text": "And make them light tonight",
      "start": 185.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 198.63999938964844,
      "text": "Find that light inside of the only way you go",
      "start": 188.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 205.27999877929688,
      "text": "Inside your only heart",
      "start": 199.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 211.3800048828125,
      "text": "Inside it's just a different star with those bitter, bitter feelin'",
      "start": 205.72000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 217.39999389648438,
      "text": "We're all a light, I can't understand why you fight",
      "start": 212.3800048828125
    },
    {
      "end": 222.24000549316406,
      "text": "Those bitter, bitter, bitter, bitter, bitter, bitter feelin'",
      "start": 217.6199951171875
    },
    {
      "end": 229.52000427246094,
      "text": "Just let them become you, no one ruins this thing you call life",
      "start": 222.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 234.13999938964844,
      "text": "You're still alive with your bitter, bitter feelin'",
      "start": 229.52000427246094
    },
    {
      "end": 240.5,
      "text": "Yes, nobody ruins this thing called life",
      "start": 234.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 242.72000122070312,
      "text": "With your bitter, bitter feelin'",
      "start": 240.5
    },
    {
      "end": 248.13999938964844,
      "text": "You think you were gone, you think it was over",
      "start": 242.72000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 254.66000366210938,
      "text": "You think, you think you'd want to run far away",
      "start": 248.72000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 260.2200012207031,
      "text": "But to stay there ignoring your only voice",
      "start": 254.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 263.67999267578125,
      "text": "Drippin' through the beginning, the ending",
      "start": 260.2200012207031
    },
    {
      "end": 264.6000061035156,
      "text": "I'll be there",
      "start": 263.67999267578125
    }
  ],
